  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provision of Shelter Kits to Returnees in Michika and Madagali LGAs Adamawa State.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is targeted to most shelter vulnerable returnees affected by the activities of insurgency for early recovery and improved living condition this will be carried out in the North Eastern  LGAs  of Michika and Madagali in Adamawa State
This will involve providing returnees with Shelter Kits and Conditional cash for labour in two tranches 40% of cash before use of kits and 60% after monitoring and evaluation of the implementation by the beneficiaries.</narrative>
  </description>
